\PYG{k}{6.} The \PYG{l+s+sb}{`background\PYGZus{}rewritten\PYGZus{}context`} should contain only the background information of the primary entity from the rewritten context, you shoudl mention the entity profile in it. No events, scenarios, or other information that is not background information of the primary entity.
